[Shipping Agents Management API] --> [ShippingAgentsController]
[Shipping Agents Management API] --> [ShippingAgentMapper]
[Shipping Agents Management API] --> [PortContext]
[Shipping Agents Management API] --> [ShippingAgent]
[Shipping Agents Management API] --> [CreateShippingAgentDTO]
[Shipping Agents Management API] --> [ShippingAgentDTO]

[PLMS Database] --> [Entity Framework Core]
[PLMS Database] --> [PortContext]

[External IAM Provider] --> [ASP.NET Auth Middleware]
